stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Idle
  Idle --> Composer: command dispatch from CLI/config
  Composer --> Plan: PlanRequest{preflight|snapshot}
  Composer --> Propose: ReleaseInput with proposal flow
  Composer --> Release: ReleaseInput direct release
  Composer --> Publish: PublishInput publish\n(load ReleaseRecord snapshot)
  Plan --> Propose: workflow requires proposal
  Plan --> Release: proposal optional path
  Plan --> Recovery: blocking validation
  Propose --> Release: proposal approved/merged
  Propose --> Recovery: proposal stale/failed
  Release --> ReleaseExecution: execute release materialization\n(plan applicability + source mutations)
  ReleaseExecution --> ReleaseRecord: materialization complete\nrelease state = materialized
  ReleaseExecution --> PartiallyMaterialized: partial materialization failure\n(manifest/SCM/commit/tag incomplete)
  PartiallyMaterialized --> Recovery: partial handoff + residual mutations
  ReleaseRecord --> Publish: consume ReleaseRecord\ntarget snapshot is frozen
  Publish --> CloseoutEngine: all required publish targets succeeded\nPublishRun state = published
  Publish --> PartiallyPublished: one+ targets failed\nPublishRun state = partial/failed
  PartiallyPublished --> Publish: nextAction=publish_retry_failed
  PartiallyPublished --> Recovery: unrecoverable target failure
  CloseoutEngine --> Closed: closeout completed (CloseoutRecord)
  CloseoutEngine --> Recovery: closeout failed or timeout
  Recovery --> Plan: resume after corrective action
  Recovery --> ReleaseExecution: resume from partial materialization state
  Recovery --> Publish: resume publish from PublishRun
  Recovery --> CloseoutEngine: resume closeout
  Closed --> [*]
